HPCU Bi-Weekly Challenge: Distributed Ideal Gas
MPI version
README
Author: Aaron Weeden, Shodor Education Foundation

To compile this program, run the following command in this directory:

make

To run the program, run the following command in this directory.  Replace the
letter X with the number of processes you wish to use.  Replace the letter Y
with the path to the machine file:

mpirun -np X --machinefile Y ./ideal-gas

The program generates ASCII output of the simulation, and a large Terminal
window may be needed to view it properly.

To remove the files generated during compilation, run the following command:

make clean

